data.description: Beautiful MOVE IN READY 5 bedroom home with 2.5 baths and separate entrance for basement for in law unit! Main level has been totally redone into an open floor concept. 1st Floor boasts 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths all new stainless steel appliances. Lower level features living area, full kitchen with dining area, 2 bedrooms and full bathroom. Roof replaced in 2017, New windows 2017, AC 2019 and Hot water heater 2021. Close to shopping, restaurants and public transportation. LOW TAXES! FHA Welcomed!
